name: 伊丽莎白·莫伊
name_full: 伊丽莎白·莫伊 Elizabeth Moy
introduction: Elizabeth is a Chinese-Canadian Actor from Vancouver BC. She was born in Kowloon Hong Kong and immigrated to Canada in the 70's with her family. Her unique personality is a by-product of both Chinese and Canadian cultures. She is fluent in both Cantonese and English; she also speaks Conversational Mandarin. Elizabeth loves all kinds of music with special interests in Classical largely due to her piano training.She obtained her Bachelor of Arts from the University of British Columbia and her Master of Arts in Organizational Management from the University of Phoenix. After over 20+ years in the corporate world, she decided to pursue her dream in acting.She fell in love with the filming industry while she was doing background performance work. She then started training in acting since 2019 with various acting teachers and studios. In 2021, Elizabeth booked her first TV series FROM (an Epix/MGM production) playing Tian-Chen. Elizabeth is excited about embarking this journey as an actor in making stories!
